### Test Likes API
GET http://localhost:3001/api/likes?slug=test-post

### Increment Likes
POST http://localhost:3001/api/likes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "test-post"
}

### Test Site Stats
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stats/site

### Test Post Views
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stats/test-post?type=view

### Increment Post View
POST http://localhost:3001/api/stats/test-post?type=view
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visitorId": "test-visitor-123"
}